Basil thanks supporters: & quot; Haida stream servers & quot;
03 Nov 2019, 17:03 by Lebanon 24
President of the Free Patriotic Movement tweeted that Gebran Bassil, Minister of Foreign Affairs in the caretaker government, tweeted: “Thanks to every young man and boy who met us today in Baabda without any insult and no collision. Server stream. "
